sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / API Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as KServe Controller Manager
    participant StorageInit as Storage Initializer<br/>(Init Container)
    participant CloudStorage as Cloud Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KnativeGW as Knative Local Gateway<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant OSRoute as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,CloudStorage: Flow 1: Model Deployment (InferenceService Creation)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated CR (defaults applied)
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-serving-kserve-io-v1beta1-inferenceservice<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
        K8sAPI-->>User: CR created

        Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment/KnativeService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create VirtualService/Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Token

        Note over StorageInit,CloudStorage: Init Container downloads model
        StorageInit->>CloudStorage: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials (IAM/keys)
        CloudStorage-->>StorageInit: Model artifacts
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,Predictor: Flow 2: Inference Request (Serverless Mode)
        User->>IstioGW: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: None/Bearer Token
        IstioGW->>KnativeGW: Forward request<br/>80/TCP HTTP<br/>Encryption: mTLS (Istio)
        KnativeGW->>Predictor: Inference request<br/>80/TCP HTTP<br/>Encryption: mTLS (Istio)
        Predictor-->>KnativeGW: Prediction response
        KnativeGW-->>IstioGW: Response
        IstioGW-->>User: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,Predictor: Flow 3: Inference Request (Raw Deployment + Auth)
        User->>OSRoute: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        OSRoute->>OAuthProxy: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (serving cert)<br/>Auth: OpenShift OAuth
        OAuthProxy->>Predictor: Forward to predictor<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)<br/>Auth: None (trusted proxy)
        Predictor-->>OAuthProxy: Prediction response
        OAuthProxy-->>OSRoute: Response
        OSRoute-->>User: JSON Response
    end
